Correlation of program and personal factors to satisfaction

Choose a question group to view how different factors correlate to satisfaction of the program.

The top left scatter plot appears in alongside individual question breakdowns. It represents all questions' correlation rating. Highly correlated facotors appear in the top right of the plot.

Individual questions are shown to the the right and below the first plot. They are arranged highest to lowest from left to right and top to bottom. The scale is as follows:

  • Strongly Disagree: -1.5; Disagree: -0.5; Agree: 0.5; Strongly Agree: 1.5
